        <part updateMethod="0" lastModifyTime="0">
            <t index="1" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:03,950</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:08,575</end-time>
                <translation>16世纪初 意大利·佛罗伦萨</translation>
                <original>16世紀初頭イタリア・フィレンゼ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="2" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:10,560</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:15,850</end-time>
                <translation>有一本被称为权谋术数之书而遭禁的著作</translation>
                <original>権謀術数の書と呼ばれ禁書とされた一冊の本がありました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="3" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:15,850</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:17,000</end-time>
                <translation>那就是《君主论》
君主論です</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="4" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:19,750</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:25,100</end-time>
                <translation>作者是外交官尼科洛·马基雅维利</translation>
                <original>作者は外交官ニッコロ・マキャベリー</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="5" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:25,100</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:26,200</end-time>
                <translation>历经500年</translation>
                <original>500年にわたって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="6" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:26,200</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:29,720</end-time>
                <translation>被各国领导者争相阅读的《君主论》</translation>
                <original>様々な国のリーダーたちが手に取ってきたという君主論</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="7" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:34,370</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:39,975</end-time>
                <translation>其中也蕴含着对现代人有所启发的提示</translation>
                <original>そこには現代の私たちにも通じるヒントがあります</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="8" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:39,975</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:42,000</end-time>
                <translation>100分de名著《君主论》</translation>
                <original>100分で名著君主論</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="9" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:45,150</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:48,440</end-time>
                <translation>指导老师是翻译《马基雅维利全集》的
指南役はマキャベリ全集の翻訳を手掛けた</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="10" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:48,440</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:50,625</end-time>
                <translation>竹田芳美老师</translation>
                <original>竹田芳美さん</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="11" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:50,625</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:52,802</end-time>
                <translation>这位马基雅维利本人也果敢地</translation>
                <original>このマキャベリー自身も果敢に</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="12" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:52,802</start-time>
                <end-time>00:00:56,400</end-time>
                <translation>直面自己的命运</translation>
                <original>自らの運命に向かい合っているということなんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="13" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:00:56,400</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:01,350</end-time>
                <translation>正因如此才写下了这部《君主论》</translation>
                <original>それがこの君主論を書いたということなんですよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="14" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:01,350</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:06,440</end-time>
                <translation>第1回将解读马基雅维利倾注在《君主论》中的真意</translation>
                <original>第1回は君主論に込められたマキャベリーの真意を読み解きます</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="15" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:30,900</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:36,375</end-time>
                <translation>第1回 “做自立的人 去活吧！”
第1回　「自立した人間として生きろ」</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="16" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:40,700</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:42,900</end-time>
                <translation>人人都曾想过要读一次</translation>
                <original>誰もが一度読んでみたいと思いながら</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="17" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:42,900</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:45,300</end-time>
                <translation>却迟迟未能翻阅的名著</translation>
                <original>なかなか手に取ることのできない名著を</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="18" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:45,325</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:47,100</end-time>
                <translation>用25分钟一集 共4集</translation>
                <original>25分かける4回つまり</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="19" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:47,150</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:50,600</end-time>
                <translation>也就是用100分钟通俗易懂地解读的《100分de名著》　</translation>
                <original>100分でわかりやすく読み解く100分で名著</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="20" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:50,600</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:51,675</end-time>
                <translation>泷口友里奈
瀧口友里奈です</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="21" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:51,694</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:54,250</end-time>
                <translation>那么本月我们要解读的是这本</translation>
                <original>さあ今回読み解いていくのはこちらです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="22" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:54,250</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:56,650</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利的《君主论》</translation>
                <original>マキャベリーの君主論</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="23" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:56,650</start-time>
                <end-time>00:01:59,480</end-time>
                <translation>泷口小姐 您肯定读过吧</translation>
                <original>滝口さんもちろん読んだことありますよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="24" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:01:59,480</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:02,925</end-time>
                <translation>哎呀 其实我还没读过呢</translation>
                <original>いやーそれが読んだことないんですよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="25" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:02,925</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:06,220</end-time>
                <translation>不过 《君主论》一般人会去读吗</translation>
                <original>でもなかなか君主論って読みますかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="26" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:06,220</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:07,300</end-time>
                <translation>我也不会读</translation>
                <original>読みません私も</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="27" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:07,300</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:08,300</end-time>
                <translation>感觉很难懂吧</translation>
                <original>難しそうですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="28" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:08,300</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:10,650</end-time>
                <translation>作为历史的知识点
歴史上のね出来事としては</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="29" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:10,650</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:14,083</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利的《君主论》是必然会出现</translation>
                <original>必ず出てくるマキャベリー 君主論なんだけども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="30" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:14,083</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:16,000</end-time>
                <translation>但我想读过的人应该不多</translation>
                <original>これを読んでる方も少ないかと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="31" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:16,000</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:17,880</end-time>
                <translation>毕竟相当难</translation>
                <original>思うんですがこれいろいろなかなかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="32" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:17,880</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:20,924</end-time>
                <translation>其中似乎有很多富有洞见的文章</translation>
                <original>含蓄のある文章がたくさんあるようですので</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="33" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:20,924</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:24,961</end-time>
                <translation>今天我们有幸请到了指南役整备学园短期大学
今日はねご指南役整備学園短期大学</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="34" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:24,961</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:27,830</end-time>
                <translation>副教授武田好美女士</translation>
                <original>準教授武田よしみさんにお越しいただいて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="35" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:27,830</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:29,760</end-time>
                <translation>来为我们深入讲解 请多关照</translation>
                <original>いろいろと語っていただきますよろしくお願いします</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="36" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:29,760</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:31,825</end-time>
                <translation>请多关照</translation>
                <original>よろしくお願いします</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="37" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:31,825</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:33,360</end-time>
                <translation>非常感谢 请多关照</translation>
                <original>どうもよろしくお願いいたします</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="38" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:36,935</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:42,450</end-time>
                <translation>研究意大利文化和语言的武田好美女士</translation>
                <original>イタリアの文化や言語を研究している武田よしみさん</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="39" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:42,450</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:46,000</end-time>
                <translation>曾翻译过马基雅维利的全集和评论</translation>
                <original>マキャベリーの全集や評論の翻訳を手掛け</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="40" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:46,000</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:48,735</end-time>
                <translation>向我们介绍了他全新的一面</translation>
                <original>その新たな一面を紹介してきました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="41" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:53,960</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:56,550</end-time>
                <translation>老师 有“马基雅维利主义（Machiavellism）”这个词对吧</translation>
                <original>先生そのマキャベリーズムっていう言葉ありますけれども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="42" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:56,550</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:59,600</end-time>
                <translation>比如为了目的不择手段</translation>
                <original>例えばその目的のために手段は選ばないとかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="43" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:02:59,600</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:02,465</end-time>
                <translation>或者说政治家擅长权谋术数</translation>
                <original>政治家は権謀術数に長けてるとかいう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="44" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:02,465</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:06,236</end-time>
                <translation>“马基雅维利主义”通常被当作这样的词来使用</translation>
                <original>そういう言葉としてマキャベリズムって使われてると思うんですけども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="45" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:06,236</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:09,050</end-time>
                <translation>这个词就是源自马基雅维利的吗？</translation>
                <original>これもやっぱりマキャベリから来ている言葉なんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="46" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:09,050</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:11,741</end-time>
                <translation>是的 “马基雅维利主义”这个词</translation>
                <original>そうなんですマキャベリズムという言葉は</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="47" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:11,741</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:15,200</end-time>
                <translation>当然是从《君主论》衍生出来的</translation>
                <original>もちろんこの君主論から発生してできた言葉なんですけれども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="48" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:15,200</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:19,275</end-time>
                <translation>但这本书里并没有直接出现这个词</translation>
                <original>この書物の中にはそのものズバリの言葉はないんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="49" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:19,275</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:22,600</end-time>
                <translation>或许存在一些被曲解的地方</translation>
                <original>ひょっとすると曲解されているところもあるかもしれません</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="50" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:22,600</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:26,422</end-time>
                <translation>但是 在将政治与宗教分离</translation>
                <original>けれどその政治と宗教を切り離して</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="51" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:26,422</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:28,925</end-time>
                <translation>并阐述政治学这一点上</translation>
                <original>政治学について述べたという点で</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="52" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:28,925</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:32,550</end-time>
                <translation>《君主论》被认为是近代政治学的奠基之作</translation>
                <original>この君主論は近代政治学の祖と言われているんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="53" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:32,550</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:33,600</end-time>
                <translation>原来如此</translation>
                <original>なるほどね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="54" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:33,600</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:36,250</end-time>
                <translation>因此 我认为从新的视角</translation>
                <original>ですからその新しい視点で</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="55" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:36,250</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:40,725</end-time>
                <translation>- 重新解读它也是可能的- 原来如此</translation>
                <original>-もう一度読み解いていくこともできるんじゃないかと思っています-なるほど</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="56" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:40,725</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:42,772</end-time>
                <translation>话说回来 这本《君主论》</translation>
                <original>そもそもその君主論というのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="57" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:42,772</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:45,975</end-time>
                <translation>我们虽然都没读过</translation>
                <original>我々もねそれを読んだこともないんですけども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="58" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:45,975</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:48,100</end-time>
                <translation>但该说它是一本怎样的书呢？</translation>
                <original>どういう本だと言ったらいいんでしょうかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="59" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:48,100</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:51,714</end-time>
                <translation>好的 正好是在16世纪初的意大利</translation>
                <original>はいちょうどその16世紀初頭のイタリアなんですが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="60" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:51,714</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:54,450</end-time>
                <translation>一位在佛罗伦萨担任外交官</translation>
                <original>そのフィレンツェ国で外交官をしていた</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="61" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:54,450</start-time>
                <end-time>00:03:56,500</end-time>
                <translation>名叫尼科洛·马基雅维利的人</translation>
                <original>ニッコロマキャベリという人が</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="62" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:03:56,500</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:00,223</end-time>
                <translation>写给当时佛罗伦萨政治的最高指挥官</translation>
                <original>当時のフィレンツェの政治の最高指揮官に向けて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="63" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:00,223</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:02,000</end-time>
                <translation>这本书是专门写给那个人的</translation>
                <original>その人に当てて書いたものなんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="64" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:02,000</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:06,780</end-time>
                <translation>外交官写给当时的所谓领袖的</translation>
                <original>外交官がその時のいわゆるリーダーに向けて書いたという</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="65" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:06,780</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:08,197</end-time>
                <translation>是的 没错</translation>
                <original>はいそうなんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="66" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:08,197</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:10,680</end-time>
                <translation>那里面写了些什么内容呢？</translation>
                <original>それはどんな内容が書かれているんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="67" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:10,680</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:13,236</end-time>
                <translation>实际上 在《君主论》中</translation>
                <original>実際にはその君主論の中には</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="68" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:13,236</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:15,738</end-time>
                <translation>有成为君主的实践方法</translation>
                <original>君主になるための実践</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="69" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:15,738</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:19,175</end-time>
                <translation>以及思想 这就是它的内容</translation>
                <original>それから思想そういうものが書かれていると思ってください</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="70" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:19,175</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:19,900</end-time>
                <translation>具体来说
具体的に言うと</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="71" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:19,900</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:23,800</end-time>
                <translation>嗯 大致可以分为四点 我们来看看</translation>
                <original>はい大きく分けると実は4つあります見てみましょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="72" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:23,800</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:25,325</end-time>
                <translation>请看这边</translation>
                <original>こちらです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="73" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:25,325</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:30,100</end-time>
                <translation>第一点 国家的分类及其征服与维持的手段
まず1つ目国の分類とその制服維持の手段</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="74" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:30,100</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:34,250</end-time>
                <translation>第二点 关于进攻与防卫的军事层面
2つ目攻撃と防衛に関する軍事的側面</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="75" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:34,250</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:36,550</end-time>
                <translation>第三点 君主的资质
3つ目君主の資質</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="76" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:36,550</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:42,000</end-time>
                <translation>然后是第四点 等待着君主的命运论</translation>
                <original>それから4つ目が君主を待ち受ける運命論ということです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="77" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:42,000</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:44,275</end-time>
                <translation>征服之类的</translation>
                <original>制服とかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="78" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:44,275</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:46,775</end-time>
                <translation>还有维持的手段之类的</translation>
                <original>なんか維持の手段とか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="79" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:46,775</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:49,105</end-time>
                <translation>以及关于防卫的军事层面等等
あと防衛に関する軍事的側面とか</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="80" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:49,105</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:52,100</end-time>
                <translation>写得相当具体 是具体地写出来的吗？</translation>
                <original>かなり具体的なことが具体的に書かれているんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="81" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:52,100</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:53,825</end-time>
                <translation>是的呢</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="82" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:53,825</start-time>
                <end-time>00:04:58,314</end-time>
                <translation>嗯 这与之前时代所写的君主论</translation>
                <original>まあそれはそれまでの時代に書かれてきた君主論とは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="83" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:04:58,314</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:00,975</end-time>
                <translation>内容大相径庭</translation>
                <original>かなり違っている内容なので</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="84" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:00,975</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:04,650</end-time>
                <translation>所以也有些标新立异的部分</translation>
                <original>ちょっと異色の部分もあったんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="85" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:04,650</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:07,420</end-time>
                <translation>我听说它后来成了禁书</translation>
                <original>発禁処分になったというふうに聞いてますけれども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="86" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:07,420</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:08,350</end-time>
                <translation>没错</translation>
                <original>そうなんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="87" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:08,350</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:10,400</end-time>
                <translation>当时果然还是认为那是一本危险的书</translation>
                <original>それをやっぱり危ない書であったの当時</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="88" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:10,400</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:11,500</end-time>
                <translation>说得没错</translation>
                <original>そうですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="89" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:11,500</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:13,363</end-time>
                <translation>基督教会认为</translation>
                <original>キリスト教教会からは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="90" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:13,363</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:15,640</end-time>
                <translation>这本书会给人们带来危害</translation>
                <original>これは人々に害を与えるということで</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="91" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:15,640</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:17,650</end-time>
                <translation>因此将其列为禁书</translation>
                <original>禁書処分になったんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="92" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:17,650</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:21,875</end-time>
                <translation>那么 我们先看看在此之前别的的君主论是什么样的</translation>
                <original>それでこの以前に書かれた君主論というものを見てみたいと思います</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="93" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:21,875</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:24,400</end-time>
                <translation>之前有别人写过类似的书吗？是的</translation>
                <original>以前に書かれた違う人が書いた人があるんですかそうなんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="94" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:24,400</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:28,140</end-time>
                <translation>有位意大利的人文学者 名叫彼特拉克</translation>
                <original>このイタリアの人文学者でペトラルカというんですが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="95" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:28,140</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:31,650</end-time>
                <translation>他是14世纪的人文主义者
14世紀の人文主義者ですね</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="96" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:31,650</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:33,875</end-time>
                <translation>他这样写道：</translation>
                <original>こんなふうに書いています</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="97" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:33,875</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:37,450</end-time>
                <translation>君主对全体臣民一视同仁的正义
君主は分け隔てのない領民への正義</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="98" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:37,450</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:39,200</end-time>
                <translation>与慈爱才是最重要的
慈愛こそが大切</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="99" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:39,200</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:40,900</end-time>
                <translation>这是他的观点</translation>
                <original>こう言っているんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="100" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:40,900</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:43,775</end-time>
                <translation>确实感觉很有道理</translation>
                <original>なるほどという感じですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="101" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:43,775</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:46,320</end-time>
                <translation>我们来看看马基雅维利是怎么说的</translation>
                <original>マキャベリはどういうふうに言っているか見てみましょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="102" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:46,320</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:49,200</end-time>
                <translation>在这里</translation>
                <original>こちらです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="103" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:49,200</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:51,375</end-time>
                <translation>冷酷与仁慈</translation>
                <original>冷酷さと憐れみ深さ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="104" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:51,375</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:56,275</end-time>
                <translation>令人畏惧与受人爱戴 究竟哪个更好？</translation>
                <original>恐れられるのと愛されるのとさてどちらが良いか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="105" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:56,275</start-time>
                <end-time>00:05:59,500</end-time>
                <translation>说到冷酷与仁慈 </translation>
                <original>冷酷さと憐れみ深さでしたら</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="106" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:05:59,500</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:01,411</end-time>
                <translation>仁慈的君主才是好君主
憐れみ深い君主の方が</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="107" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:01,411</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:03,675</end-time>
                <translation>这是我们常有的想法</translation>
                <original>良い君主という感じがしてしまうんですが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="108" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:03,675</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:04,247</end-time>
                <translation>是的</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="109" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:04,247</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:05,720</end-time>
                <translation>虽然大家都会这么想 </translation>
                <original>そう思うんですけれども</original>
                <spell/>
