                <end-time>00:06:22,774</end-time>
                <translation>哦——</translation>
                <original>はー</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="122" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:22,774</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:24,219</end-time>
                <translation>既然如此</translation>
                <original>何のにもかかわらず</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="123" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:24,219</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:25,976</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利为什么要特意</translation>
                <original>マキャベリはわざわざ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="124" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:25,976</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:28,480</end-time>
                <translation>出版这样一本书呢？</translation>
                <original>こういう本をどうして出版することになったんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="125" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:28,480</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:29,069</end-time>
                <translation>这个嘛</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="126" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:29,069</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:32,960</end-time>
                <translation>这与他当时所处的时代背景</translation>
                <original>それはちょうど彼が生きていたこの当時の時代背景と</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="127" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:32,960</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:34,940</end-time>
                <translation>以及他曾担任外交官</translation>
                <original>彼が外交官だったっていう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="128" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:34,940</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:37,752</end-time>
                <translation>这一职业有着很大的关系</translation>
                <original>そういう職業にも大きく関わっていると思いますね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="129" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:37,752</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:40,048</end-time>
                <translation>外交官 原来如此</translation>
                <original>外交官なるほどね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="130" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:40,048</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:42,132</end-time>
                <translation>那么 关于马基雅维利的人生</translation>
                <original>さあそれではマキャベリの人生</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="131" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:42,132</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:44,772</end-time>
                <translation>以及《君主论》诞生的时代背景</translation>
                <original>そして君主論が生まれた時代背景について</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="132" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:44,772</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:46,040</end-time>
                <translation>我们通过一段VTR来了解一下吧</translation>
                <original>ちょっとVTRで見ていきましょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="133" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:49,325</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:50,844</end-time>
                <translation>《君主论》的作者</translation>
                <original>君主論の作者</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="134" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:50,844</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:53,059</end-time>
                <translation>尼科洛·马基雅维利出生于</translation>
                <original>ニッコロ・マキャベリが生まれたのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="135" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:53,059</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:55,156</end-time>
                <translation>15世纪的意大利</translation>
                <original>15世紀イタリア</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="136" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:06:55,156</start-time>
                <end-time>00:06:57,180</end-time>
                <translation>被誉为花之都的佛罗伦萨共和国</translation>
                <original>花の都と呼ばれたフィレンツェ国</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="137" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:00,456</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:02,540</end-time>
                <translation>当时统治这个国家的是</translation>
                <original>当時国を統治していたのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="138" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:02,540</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:05,985</end-time>
                <translation>经营金融业的洛伦佐·德·美第奇</translation>
                <original>金融業を営んでいたロレンツォ・デ・メディチです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="139" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:08,696</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:11,785</end-time>
                <translation>佛罗伦萨作为商业城市繁荣发展</translation>
                <original>フィレンツェは商業都市として栄え</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="140" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:11,785</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:13,844</end-time>
                <translation>在热爱艺术的洛伦佐的推动下</translation>
                <original>芸術を愛したロレンツォによって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="141" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:13,844</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:16,884</end-time>
                <translation>迎来了文艺复兴文化的最盛期</translation>
                <original>ルネサンス文化の最盛期を迎えました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="142" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:25,922</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:28,742</end-time>
                <translation>但是在1492年</translation>
                <original>しかし1492年</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="143" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:28,742</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:30,767</end-time>
                <translation>洛伦佐·德·美第奇去世后</translation>
                <original>ロレンツォでメディチが亡くなり</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="144" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:30,767</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:32,380</end-time>
                <translation>情况发生了巨变
状況が一変します</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="145" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:35,076</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:38,166</end-time>
                <translation>当时的意大利分裂成多个国家</translation>
                <original>当時イタリアはいくつもの国に分かれ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="146" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:38,166</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:42,418</end-time>
                <translation>处于各方都企图扩张领土的群雄割据时代
それぞれが領土拡大を狙う群雄割拠の時代</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="147" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:42,418</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:45,080</end-time>
                <translation>此外 法国、西班牙等国</translation>
                <original>さらにフランス、スペインなどが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="148" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:45,080</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:47,213</end-time>
                <translation>也正谋划着入侵意大利</translation>
                <original>イタリア侵攻を目論んでいました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="149" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:51,766</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:53,599</end-time>
                <translation>失去了领导人的佛罗伦萨</translation>
                <original>リーダー不在のフィレンツェは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="150" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:53,599</start-time>
                <end-time>00:07:55,520</end-time>
                <translation>开始剧烈动荡</translation>
                <original>大きく揺れ始めます</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="151" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:07:58,683</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:01,785</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利被任命为政府秘书官</translation>
                <original>マキャベリーが政府の初期間に任命されたのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="152" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:01,785</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:03,760</end-time>
                <translation>正是在那个时候</translation>
                <original>ちょうどその頃</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="153" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:03,760</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:07,640</end-time>
                <translation>1498年 他29岁</translation>
                <original>1498年、29歳の時でした</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="154" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:11,255</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:15,193</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利并非出身名门贵族</translation>
                <original>マキャベリーは名門貴族の出身ではありませんでしたが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="155" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:15,193</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:17,687</end-time>
                <translation>但凭借天生的聪明才智和行动力
生来の頭の良さと行動力で</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="156" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:17,687</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:20,420</end-time>
                <translation>很快便获得了高层的信任</translation>
                <original>たちまち上層部の信頼を得ていきます</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="157" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:24,554</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:26,341</end-time>
                <translation>在动荡的时代
激動の時代</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="158" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:26,341</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:29,393</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利为国效力了15年</translation>
                <original>マキャベリーは15年間国に使えました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="159" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:33,477</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:35,916</end-time>
                <translation>活用这些经验写成的</translation>
                <original>その経験を生かして書かれたのが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="160" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:35,916</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:37,280</end-time>
                <translation>就是《君主论》</translation>
                <original>君主論なのです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="161" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:43,054</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:46,411</end-time>
                <translation>这就是当时的意大利</translation>
                <original>これが当時のイタリアということになります</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="162" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:46,411</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:48,705</end-time>
                <translation>如此四分五裂 群雄割据</translation>
                <original>こんなに分かれていた群雄割拠であり</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="163" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:48,705</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:51,483</end-time>
                <translation>同时也面临着来自法国、西班牙等国的威胁</translation>
                <original>フランスとかスペインの脅威も感じていたと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="164" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:51,483</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:52,839</end-time>
                <translation>这样一个情况</translation>
                <original>いうことですけれども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="165" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:52,839</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:54,781</end-time>
                <translation>当时马基雅维利是在这个弗洛伦萨吧</translation>
                <original>このマキャベリーのいたフィレンツェですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="166" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:54,781</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:55,484</end-time>
                <translation>是的</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="167" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:55,484</start-time>
                <end-time>00:08:57,627</end-time>
                <translation>当时是怎样一种状况呢</translation>
                <original>これは当時どういう状況だったんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="168" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:08:57,627</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:00,240</end-time>
                <translation>是的 在洛伦佐·德·美第奇去世后</translation>
                <original>はいロレンゾでメーディチ亡き後</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="169" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:00,240</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:03,418</end-time>
                <translation>那可以说是一个领导者缺席的时代</translation>
                <original>いわばリーダーが不在の時代だったんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="170" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:03,418</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:05,080</end-time>
                <translation>来自阿尔卑斯山另一侧</translation>
                <original>アルプスの向こう側から</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="171" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:05,080</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:08,140</end-time>
                <translation>法国和西班牙的势力开始波及</translation>
                <original>フランスやスペインの勢力が及ぶような</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="172" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:08,140</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:12,223</end-time>
                <translation>正是这样一个巨大的转折期</translation>
                <original>そういう大転換期だったわけですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="173" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:12,223</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:15,237</end-time>
                <translation>从某种意义上说 前景非常不明朗</translation>
                <original>ある意味非常に先行きの見えない</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="174" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:15,237</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:16,760</end-time>
                <translation>处于一种不稳定的状态
不安定な状態というと</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="175" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:16,760</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:20,676</end-time>
                <translation>感觉和现在的日本也有几分相似</translation>
                <original>今の日本にもどこか似ているような気もしないでもないし</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="176" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:20,676</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:22,936</end-time>
                <translation>从回归原点的意义上来说
原点に立ち返る意味でも</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="177" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:22,936</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:24,409</end-time>
                <translation>对于我们日本人而言</translation>
                <original>やっぱり我々日本人にとっても</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="178" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:24,409</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:25,999</end-time>
                <translation>我想今后也会很有学习价值</translation>
                <original>これから勉強になるんじゃないかと思うんですけれどもね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="179" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:25,999</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:27,060</end-time>
                <translation>我也这么认为</translation>
                <original>そう思います</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="180" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:29,983</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:33,833</end-time>
                <translation>现实主义者 马基雅维利
現実主義者　マキャベリ</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="181" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:35,278</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:37,583</end-time>
                <translation>将政治与伦理分开
政治と倫理とを切り離して</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="182" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:37,583</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:39,926</end-time>
                <translation>现在需要的是什么</translation>
                <original>今必要なことは何かという</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="183" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:39,926</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:43,994</end-time>
                <translation>他写的是现实路线的内容</translation>
                <original>現実路線のことを書いたということなんですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="184" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:43,994</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:45,551</end-time>
                <translation>然后 他是这么说的</translation>
                <original>で彼はこう言っているんですが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="185" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:45,551</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:48,715</end-time>
                <translation>自己要写对读者有用的东西</translation>
                <original>読む人の役に立つものを自分は書くんだ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="186" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:49,451</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:50,540</end-time>
                <translation>这是他明确表达了的</translation>
                <original>そういうふうに言っています</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="187" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:50,540</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:54,238</end-time>
                <translation>所以 要写活生生的现实</translation>
                <original>ですから生々しい現実のことを書くんだ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="188" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:54,238</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:55,812</end-time>
                <translation>应该追求那样的真实</translation>
                <original>そういう真実を追うべきだというのが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="189" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:55,812</start-time>
                <end-time>00:09:58,775</end-time>
                <translation>这就是他的想法</translation>
                <original>というのは彼の考えなんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="190" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:09:58,775</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:00,460</end-time>
                <translation>关于理由 他是这么说的</translation>
                <original>その理由をこんなふうに言っています</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="191" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:00,460</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:01,257</end-time>
                <translation>好</translation>
                <original>はい</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="192" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:05,872</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:07,512</end-time>
                <translation>嗯 我们来看看</translation>
                <original>はい、みてみましょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="193" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:07,512</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:09,460</end-time>
                <translation>人实际生存的状态</translation>
                <original>人が現実に生きているのと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="194" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:09,460</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:11,720</end-time>
                <translation>与人应该如何生活</translation>
                <original>人間いかに生きるべきかというのとは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="195" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:11,720</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:14,543</end-time>
                <translation>这两者相去甚远</translation>
                <original>はなはだかけ離れている</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="196" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:14,543</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:17,087</end-time>
                <translation>因此 只看到人应该如何生活</translation>
                <original>だから人間いかに生きるべきかを見て</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="197" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:17,087</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:20,904</end-time>
                <translation>却忽略了实际生存的现实状态的人
現に人が生きている現実の姿を見逃す人間は</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="198" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:20,904</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:22,394</end-time>
                <translation>别说自立了</translation>
                <original>自立するどころか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="199" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:22,394</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:25,091</end-time>
                <translation>最终只会落得个认清破灭的下场</translation>
                <original>破滅を思い知らされるのがオチである</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="200" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:28,723</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:31,180</end-time>
                <translation>也就是说 不能只追求理想</translation>
                <original>つまり理想ばかり追っていてはいけない</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="201" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:31,180</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:32,822</end-time>
                <translation>要好好看清现实</translation>
                <original>現実をしっかり見て</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="202" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:32,822</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:35,634</end-time>
                <translation>自己能做到什么 不能做到什么</translation>
                <original>自分が何ができるのかできないのか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="203" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:35,634</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:37,820</end-time>
                <translation>应该做什么</translation>
                <original>何をすべきなのかというのを</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="204" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:37,820</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:40,560</end-time>
                <translation>把握这些是很重要的 他是在说这个</translation>
                <original>把握することが大切ですよと言っているんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="205" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:42,380</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:49,065</end-time>
                <translation>正视现实、分析、获得智慧
現実を見つめ　分析し　知恵を得る</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="206" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:49,498</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:51,280</end-time>
                <translation>真是个了不起的现实主义者啊</translation>
                <original>すごいなんかリアリストというか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="207" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:51,280</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:53,729</end-time>
                <translation>是啊 现实主义者</translation>
                <original>そうですね、現実主義者という</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="208" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:53,729</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:56,305</end-time>
                <translation>以现实与理想大相径庭</translation>
                <original>その現実を見るとやっぱり理想とはだいぶ違う</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="209" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:56,305</start-time>
                <end-time>00:10:58,416</end-time>
                <translation>这一点为前提</translation>
                <original>ということを前提に</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="210" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:10:58,416</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:02,178</end-time>
                <translation>在某种意义上作为一位分析着政治和国家的分析师</translation>
                <original>政治とか国をある意味分析しているアナリストだった</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="211" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:02,178</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:04,275</end-time>
                <translation>大概就是这样的意思吧</translation>
                <original>というふうなことなんでしょうけども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="212" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:04,275</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:05,848</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利的这种态度</translation>
                <original>マキャベリのこうした姿勢というのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="213" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:05,848</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:06,987</end-time>
                <translation>是从何而来的呢？</translation>
                <original>どこから来たものなんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="214" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:06,987</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:11,272</end-time>
                <translation>是呢 首先第一点 因为他曾是一名外交官</translation>
                <original>そうですね、まず第一に彼が外交官だったということですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="215" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:11,272</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:14,988</end-time>
                <translation>他作为外交官活跃了15年 </translation>
                <original>外交官として彼は15年間活躍したんですが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="216" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:14,988</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:16,277</end-time>
                <translation>在那期间 </translation>
                <original>その間に</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="217" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:16,277</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:20,010</end-time>
                <translation>他曾离开佛罗伦萨超过40次</translation>
                <original>40回以上フィレンチェの国の外へ出ているんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="218" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:20,010</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:21,667</end-time>
                <translation>而他前往赴任的地方 是的 </translation>
                <original>で赴任した先でそうなんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="219" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:21,667</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:23,324</end-time>
                <translation>年轻有为啊</translation>
                <original>すごい若い人ね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="220" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:23,324</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:26,900</end-time>
                <translation>而且那个时代 交通工具只有马之类的吧</translation>
                <original>しかもその時代って馬とかしか交通手段ないですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="221" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:26,900</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:27,770</end-time>
                <translation>没错</translation>
                <original>そうなんですよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="222" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:27,770</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:31,124</end-time>
                <translation>他是个骑着马、相当充满活力的人呢</translation>
                <original>馬に乗って本当に活動的な人だったんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="223" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:31,124</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:35,778</end-time>
                <translation>在那里与对方国家的君主会面</translation>
                <original>その先で相手国の君主と相まみえて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="224" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:35,778</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:37,519</end-time>
                <translation>进行外交接触 
外交接触をして</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="225" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:37,519</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:40,582</end-time>
                <translation>这关系到自己国家的存亡 这是当然</translation>
                <original>自分の国の存亡はもちろんかかっていますよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="226" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:40,582</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:42,651</end-time>
                <translation>然后收集情报</translation>
                <original>でそれで情報を集めて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="227" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:42,651</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:45,254</end-time>
                <translation>将分析、观察到的事情</translation>
                <original>分析をして観察したことを</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="228" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:45,254</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:46,675</end-time>
                <translation>整理成报告书</translation>
                <original>報告書にまとめて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="229" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:46,675</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:49,458</end-time>
                <translation>分多次送回自己的国家</translation>
                <original>何通も自国へ送り返している</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="230" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:49,458</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:50,826</end-time>
                <translation>这便是他做的事</translation>
                <original>ということなんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="231" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:50,826</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:53,195</end-time>
                <translation>将其信息和想法呈交给佛罗伦萨的政府 </translation>
                <original>それをフィレンチェの政府に示すことが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="232" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:53,195</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:54,559</end-time>
                <translation>就是他的工作</translation>
                <original>彼の仕事でしたね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="233" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:54,559</start-time>
                <end-time>00:11:57,421</end-time>
                <translation>见过各种各样的君主 见识了很多呢</translation>
                <original>いろんな君主にあっていろいろ見てきたんだね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="234" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:11:57,421</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:00,284</end-time>
                <translation>这真是一份非常有价值的工作啊</translation>
                <original>でも本当にやりがいのある仕事ですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="235" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:00,284</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:04,502</end-time>
                <translation>像这样 自己亲临政治运作的现场 
こう自分自身が政治が動く場に立ち会って</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="236" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:04,502</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:07,850</end-time>
                <translation>并且自己也做出贡献</translation>
                <original>そして自分も貢献してというのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="237" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:07,850</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:09,156</end-time>
                <translation>真是一份非常有趣的工作</translation>
                <original>すごく面白い仕事ですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="238" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:09,156</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:11,733</end-time>
                <translation>我觉得这真是一份极有妙趣的工作 </translation>
                <original>本当に醍醐味のある仕事だと思いますが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="239" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:11,733</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:13,783</end-time>
                <translation>不过 马基雅维利在工作时</translation>
                <original>マキャベリが仕事をする時に</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="240" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:13,783</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:15,840</end-time>
                <translation>有件事是他一直依赖他人的 </translation>
                <original>人を頼りにしていたことがあるんですが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="241" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:15,840</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:17,920</end-time>
                <translation>您认为那是什么呢？</translation>
                <original>それは何だと思われますか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="242" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:19,259</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:19,940</end-time>
                <translation>是什么呢？</translation>
                <original>何ですかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="243" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:19,940</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:21,624</end-time>
                <translation>不是宗教吧</translation>
                <original>宗教じゃないのね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="244" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:21,624</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:22,497</end-time>
                <translation>因为他是个相当的现实主义者</translation>
                <original>かなりリアリストですからね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="245" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:22,497</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:25,376</end-time>
                <translation>其实就在这里</translation>
                <original>実はこちらにあります</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="246" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:25,376</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:27,385</end-time>
                <translation>我们来看看吧</translation>
                <original>見てみましょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="247" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:27,385</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:30,146</end-time>
                <translation>是历史书啊</translation>
                <original>歴史書なんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="248" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:30,146</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:32,289</end-time>
                <translation>君主应亲近历史书 
君主は歴史書に親しみ</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="249" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:32,289</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:35,604</end-time>
                <translation>通过阅读 考察英杰们完成的伟业 </translation>
                <original>読書を通して英傑のしとげた行いを</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="250" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:35,604</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:37,780</end-time>
                <translation>这一点至关重要</translation>
                <original>考察することが肝心である</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="251" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:40,006</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:43,186</end-time>
                <translation>他在《君主论》中是这样阐述的</translation>
                <original>こんな風に君主論で彼は述べています</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="252" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:43,186</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:46,434</end-time>
                <translation>他的想法是 历史会重演 </translation>
                <original>彼の考えなんですが歴史は繰り返す</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="253" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:46,434</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:50,535</end-time>
                <translation>无论什么时代 人类都不会改变</translation>
                <original>いつの世も人間は変わらないということなんですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="254" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:50,535</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:53,789</end-time>
                <translation>他从年轻时起就大量阅读历史 </translation>
                <original>彼はずっと若い時から歴史をたくさん読んで</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="255" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:53,789</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:55,305</end-time>
                <translation>积累知识 
知識を重ねて</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="256" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:55,305</start-time>
                <end-time>00:12:57,720</end-time>
                <translation>通过这样的学习 </translation>
                <original>それで学んできたということによって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="257" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:12:57,720</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:02,369</end-time>
                <translation>在外交官的工作中得到了很好的运用</translation>
                <original>外交官の仕事にとても活かせていたということなんですよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="258" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:02,369</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:06,387</end-time>
                <translation>例如 在赴任地工作遇到瓶颈时 </translation>
                <original>例えば赴任した先で何か仕事に行き詰まった時には</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="259" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:06,387</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:08,720</end-time>
                <translation>他会对祖国的朋友说</translation>
                <original>母国にいる友人に歴史書</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="260" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:08,720</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:10,339</end-time>
                <translation>希望他们买些历史书寄过来</translation>
                <original>を買えて送ってほしい</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="261" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:10,339</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:12,329</end-time>
                <translation>他是这么说的</translation>
                <original>というふうに言っているんですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="262" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:13,183</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:20,115</end-time>
                <translation>从历史书中学习古人的智慧
歴史書から古代の人々の知恵を学ぶ</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="263" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:20,447</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:23,728</end-time>
                <translation>在各国游历观察到的事情 </translation>
                <original>いろいろな国に行って観察したことと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="264" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:23,728</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:25,787</end-time>
                <translation>以及历史书 也就是过去的恩师知己 对吧</translation>
                <original>それは歴史書つまり過去の恩子知心ですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="265" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:25,787</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:26,480</end-time>
                <translation>是的呢</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="266" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:26,480</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:28,968</end-time>
                <translation>也就是在探寻古训 对吧</translation>
                <original>古きを訪ねているわけですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="267" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:28,968</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:33,236</end-time>
                <translation>他将那些古人的智慧全部装入脑中 </translation>
                <original>そういう昔の人たちの知恵も全部頭の中に入れて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="268" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:33,236</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:34,308</end-time>
                <translation>然后写成了《君主论》这样呢</translation>
                <original>そして君主論を書いたということですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="269" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:34,308</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:35,128</end-time>
                <translation>是的呢</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="270" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:35,128</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:38,133</end-time>
                <translation>他从古代历史中获得的</translation>
                <original>古代の人たちの歴史から得た</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="271" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:38,133</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:39,530</end-time>
                <translation>内在学识和
彼の中身と</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="272" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:39,530</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:41,907</end-time>
                <translation>再加上他眼前所见的现实 </translation>
                <original>それから現実に目の前で見た</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="273" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:41,907</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:44,334</end-time>
                <translation>可以说他是基于这些写成的</translation>
                <original>ものから書き上げたと言っていいでしょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="274" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:44,334</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:45,372</end-time>
                <translation>原来如此</translation>
                <original>なるほどね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="275" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:47,900</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:53,249</end-time>
                <translation>君主所必需的……</translation>
                <original>君主に必要なものとは…</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="276" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:54,411</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:57,106</end-time>
                <translation>从这些种种分析中得出的 </translation>
                <original>そうしたいろいろな分析の中から出てきたのが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="277" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:57,106</start-time>
                <end-time>00:13:58,948</end-time>
                <translation>就是这个</translation>
                <original>こちらです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="278" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:13:58,948</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:03,082</end-time>
                <translation>与君主密切相关的项目有两个</translation>
                <original>君主に大きく関わりのある項目が2つ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="279" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:03,082</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:05,359</end-time>
                <translation>即力量（Virtù）与命运（Fortuna）
力量と運命です</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="280" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:05,359</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:08,171</end-time>
                <translation>这两个是关键词吗？</translation>
                <original>これ2つがキーワードになってくるんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="281" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:08,171</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:09,476</end-time>
                <translation>没错</translation>
                <original>そうなんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="282" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:09,476</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:13,260</end-time>
                <translation>是的 这里说的力量 是君主应具备的</translation>
                <original>はいこちらの力量というのは君主が持つべきもの</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="283" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:13,260</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:17,545</end-time>
                <translation>资质 比如有时也翻译成器量</translation>
                <original>資質例えば器量とも訳されたりしますね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="284" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:17,545</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:19,640</end-time>
                <translation>那这个命运又是指什么呢？</translation>
                <original>この運命というのはどういうことなんでしょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="285" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:19,640</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:22,935</end-time>
                <translation>我一直以为他是个极端的现实主义者 </translation>
                <original>すごく現実主義者だと思ってたんですけども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="286" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:22,935</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:25,127</end-time>
                <translation>原来他也重视命运吗？</translation>
                <original>運命ということも大事にしていたんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="287" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:25,127</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:26,199</end-time>
                <translation>正是如此</translation>
                <original>そうなんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="288" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:26,199</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:29,084</end-time>
                <translation>我想这有一部分是由于</translation>
                <original>これは歴史の事実から学んだ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="289" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:29,084</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:30,735</end-time>
                <translation>他是从历史事实中学到了</translation>
                <original>ということもあると思うんですが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="290" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:30,735</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:34,234</end-time>
                <translation>这也与他的人生有很大关系吧</translation>
                <original>彼の人生も大きく関わっていると思いますよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="291" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:34,234</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:35,656</end-time>
                <translation>他的命运 
彼の運命</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="292" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:35,656</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:38,887</end-time>
                <translation>以及他上司索代里尼的命运</translation>
                <original>それから彼の上司だったソデリーニの運命</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="293" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:38,887</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:44,110</end-time>
                <translation>他终究还是被上司索代里尼的命运所牵连</translation>
                <original>その上司のソデリーニの運命に彼がやはり巻き込まれてしまう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="294" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:44,110</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:46,252</end-time>
                <translation>我想是由于这些原因吧</translation>
                <original>そういうことがあったと思いますね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="295" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:46,252</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:48,370</end-time>
                <translation>包括他与上司的关系等等 </translation>
                <original>その上司との関係なんかも含めて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="296" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:48,370</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:52,128</end-time>
                <translation>请用连环画剧详细说明一下吧</translation>
                <original>紙芝居でいろいろと説明してください</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="297" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:52,128</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:53,132</end-time>
                <translation>那么请看这边</translation>
                <original>ではこちらです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="298" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:55,307</start-time>
                <end-time>00:14:57,346</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利曾作为时任国家元首</translation>
                <original>マキャベリーは時の国家元首</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="299" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:14:57,346</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:00,367</end-time>
                <translation>皮耶罗·索代里尼的秘书官而活跃</translation>
                <original>ピエロソデリーニの秘書官として活躍していました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="300" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:02,777</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:05,151</end-time>
                <translation>索代里尼是一位始终遵循法律</translation>
                <original>ソデリーニは常に法にのっとって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="301" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:05,151</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:07,210</end-time>
                <translation>来处理政务的人物
政治を行う人物でした</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="302" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:07,210</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:09,620</end-time>
                <translation>感觉像是一位贤明的君主呢</translation>
                <original>いい君主という感じがしますね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="303" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:09,620</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:10,892</end-time>
                <translation>依法行事</translation>
                <original>法にのっとって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="304" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:10,892</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:14,730</end-time>
                <translation>不久 法国和西班牙觊觎入侵意大利</translation>
                <original>やがてフランススペインがイタリアへの侵攻を狙う</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="305" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:14,730</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:16,952</end-time>
                <translation>进入了动荡不安的时代
不安定な時代に突入します</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="306" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:16,952</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:20,380</end-time>
                <translation>1512年 佛罗伦萨发生了变故</translation>
                <original>1512年フィレンツで異変が起きます</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="307" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:23,895</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:26,575</end-time>
                <translation>曾经统治此地的美第奇家族</translation>
                <original>かつてこの地を治めていたメディチ家</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="308" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:26,575</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:28,978</end-time>
                <translation>以政治复辟为条件
の政治復帰を条件にして</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="309" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:28,978</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:30,728</end-time>
                <translation>西班牙军队攻了进来</translation>
                <original>スペイン軍が攻め込んできたんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="310" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:31,665</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:33,482</end-time>
                <translation>面对兵临城下的敌人
目前に敵が迫る中</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="311" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:33,482</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:37,073</end-time>
                <translation>索德里尼无法做出任何决断</translation>
                <original>ソデリーニは何の判断も下すことができません</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="312" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:40,806</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:43,417</end-time>
                <translation>佛罗伦萨共和国迎来了终结的时刻</translation>
                <original>フィレンツ共和国は終わりの時を迎えます</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="313" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:46,898</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:50,497</end-time>
                <translation>而索德里尼本人也逃亡到了国外</translation>
                <original>そしてソデリーニ自身も国外逃亡を果たします</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="314" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:50,497</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:52,434</end-time>
                <translation>而为索德里尼尽忠的</translation>
                <original>そしてソデリーニに尽くしていた</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="315" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:52,434</start-time>
                <end-time>00:15:55,386</end-time>
                <translation>尼科洛·马基雅维利也因此失势了</translation>
                <original>ニッコロマキャベリも失脚してしまうのです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="316" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:15:58,381</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:01,394</end-time>
                <translation>本以为索德里尼是一位非常杰出的领袖</translation>
                <original>ソデリーニは非常に立派なリーダーだと思って</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="317" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:01,394</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:03,520</end-time>
                <translation>才拼命追随他的</translation>
                <original>一生懸命くっついてやってたのに</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="318" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:03,520</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:07,086</end-time>
                <translation>结果西班牙一攻进来 他就无法做出决断</translation>
                <original>スペインが攻め込んできたら判断ができなかった</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="319" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:07,086</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:09,329</end-time>
                <translation>这才明白他是个靠不住的人</translation>
                <original>これはふにゃらけた人だった</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="320" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:09,329</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:10,065</end-time>
                <translation>对吧</translation>
                <original>ってことが分かっちゃったわけですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="321" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:10,065</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:12,978</end-time>
                <translation>他当时有点优柔寡断呢</translation>
                <original>それちょっと優柔不断だったんですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="322" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:12,978</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:16,727</end-time>
                <translation>结果自己也因此失势</translation>
                <original>それで自分も結局失脚してしまうという</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="323" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:16,727</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:19,100</end-time>
                <translation>被驱逐出了佛罗伦萨</translation>
                <original>フィレンツ国から追放されてしまうんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="324" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:22,648</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:25,634</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利因莫须有的嫌疑</translation>
                <original>マキャベリは無本の容疑を受けて</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="325" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:25,634</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:27,055</end-time>
                <translation>被关进了监狱</translation>
                <original>監獄に入れられました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="326" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:28,712</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:31,190</end-time>
                <translation>尽管是冤枉的</translation>
                <original>無実の罪だったにもかかわらず</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="327" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:31,190</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:32,760</end-time>
                <translation>甚至还遭受了拷问</translation>
                <original>拷問まで受けたのです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="328" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:35,069</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:37,634</end-time>
                <translation>一年后才获释</translation>
                <original>釈放されたのは1年後</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="329" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:37,634</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:39,660</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利失去了工作</translation>
                <original>マキャベリは職を失い</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="330" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:39,660</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:40,849</end-time>
                <translation>在失意之中
失意の中で</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="331" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:40,849</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:44,280</end-time>
                <translation>被迫在佛罗伦萨郊外的山庄生活</translation>
                <original>フィレンツ郊外の山荘暮らしを余儀なくされたのです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="332" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:48,263</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:50,040</end-time>
                <translation>那是马基雅维利多少岁时的事？</translation>
                <original>それってマキャベリがいくつの時だったんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="333" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:50,040</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:52,649</end-time>
                <translation>他当时正好44岁</translation>
                <original>ちょうど彼は44歳だったんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="334" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:52,649</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:54,457</end-time>
                <translation>才44岁啊</translation>
                <original>まだ44歳ですよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="335" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:54,457</start-time>
                <end-time>00:16:55,680</end-time>
                <translation>正值壮年呢</translation>
                <original>働き盛りですよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="336" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:16:55,680</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:00,536</end-time>
                <translation>- 却和主君的命运一起 - 失势了</translation>
                <original>-なのにボスの運命と一緒に　-失脚と</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="337" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:00,567</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:02,341</end-time>
                <translation>从荣耀的巅峰一落千丈
栄光から一転と</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="338" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:02,341</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:04,573</end-time>
                <translation>被逐出政界这件事 </translation>
                <original>この政界から追放されたことで</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="339" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:04,573</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:07,246</end-time>
                <translation>让他受到了相当大的打击</translation>
                <original>彼はかなり傷ついてしまったんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="340" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:07,246</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:10,895</end-time>
                <translation>那可是他拼命效忠的国家啊</translation>
                <original>一生懸命自分が尽くしてきた国ですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="341" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:10,895</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:14,795</end-time>
                <translation>而且他还是个不折不扣的工作狂</translation>
                <original>しかも大変な仕事人間だったんですからね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="342" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:14,795</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:18,846</end-time>
                <translation>于是 他回顾自己的人生 </translation>
                <original>で彼はこういう自分自身の人生を振り返って</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="343" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:18,846</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:21,723</end-time>
                <translation>世人都认为世界由命运和神支配 </translation>
                <original>世界は運命と神に支配されていると</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="344" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:21,723</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:23,215</end-time>
                <translation>世人都这么想 </translation>
                <original>世間の人が思っているけど</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="345" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:23,215</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:25,592</end-time>
                <translation>而自己也不禁会这么认为</translation>
                <original>自分も同じように思ってしまう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="346" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:25,592</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:27,350</end-time>
                <translation>他有这么说过</translation>
                <original>そんな風に言っていますね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="347" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:27,350</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:30,312</end-time>
                <translation>但他也说君主则不然</translation>
                <original>けれど君主たるものは違うと言っているんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="348" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:30,312</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:31,860</end-time>
                <translation>请看这里</translation>
                <original>それがこちらです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="349" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:31,860</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:34,045</end-time>
                <translation>他说身为君主则不然吗？</translation>
                <original>君主たるものは違うと言っているんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="350" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:34,045</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:34,699</end-time>
                <translation>是的 我们来说说看</translation>
                <original>はい、言ってみましょう</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="351" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:37,209</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:40,674</end-time>
                <translation>（第25章）完全依赖命运的君主 
（25章）全面的に運命に依存してしまう君主は</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="352" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:40,674</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:45,167</end-time>
                <translation>一旦命运变化就会灭亡</translation>
                <original>運命が変われば滅びるということ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="353" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:45,167</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:50,533</end-time>
                <translation>此外 让自己的做法与时代保持一致的人会成功 </translation>
                <original>また時世とともに自分のやり方を 一致させた人は成功し</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="354" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:50,533</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:54,249</end-time>
                <translation>反之 时代与自己的生存方式不合拍的人 </translation>
                <original>逆に時代と自分の生き方が噛み合わないものは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="355" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:54,249</start-time>
                <end-time>00:17:55,798</end-time>
                <translation>就会遭遇不幸</translation>
                <original>不幸になるということ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="356" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:17:59,162</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:01,246</end-time>
                <translation>但是 虽说是君主 </translation>
                <original>でもいくら君主といえども</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="357" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:01,246</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:04,427</end-time>
                <translation>他认为命运可以凭自己改变吗？</translation>
                <original>運命が自分でどうにかなると言っているんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="358" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:04,427</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:07,340</end-time>
                <translation>所谓命运 不就是那种不可抗力、无可奈何的东西吗？</translation>
                <original>なんか不可抗力でどうしようもないようなのが運命じゃないですかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="359" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:07,340</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:08,093</end-time>
                <translation>没错呢</translation>
                <original>そうですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="360" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:08,093</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:10,922</end-time>
                <translation>但是 他把这个命运 </translation>
                <original>でも彼はこの運命というものを</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="361" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:10,922</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:14,186</end-time>
                <translation>用河流来打比方呢</translation>
                <original>川の流れに例えているんですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="362" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:14,186</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:17,835</end-time>
                <translation>即使是肆虐的河流 也可以筑起堤坝</translation>
                <original>猛威を振る川でもせきを作って</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="363" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:17,835</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:19,291</end-time>
                <translation>通过修建堤坝</translation>
                <original>包みを作って</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="364" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:19,291</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:22,620</end-time>
                <translation>这样一来 不就能提前做好准备了吗？</translation>
                <original>そうすればあらかじめ備えていくことはできるんじゃないか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="365" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:22,620</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:24,447</end-time>
                <translation>他是这么说的</translation>
                <original>そんな風に言っています</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="366" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:24,447</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:27,589</end-time>
                <translation>也就是说 如果索德里尼也有这种先见之明的话 </translation>
                <original>ソデリーにもその先見の目を持っていれば</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="367" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:27,589</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:29,837</end-time>
                <translation>结果可能就会不同了吧</translation>
                <original>また違ったかもしれないということですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="368" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:29,837</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:31,200</end-time>
                <translation>是呢</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="369" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:31,200</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:33,000</end-time>
                <translation>原来如此</translation>
                <original>そうか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="370" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:33,000</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:36,181</end-time>
                <translation>他说不能呆呆地接受命运</translation>
                <original>ぼーっと運命を受け入れていたらダメだと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="371" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:36,181</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:37,068</end-time>
                <translation>是的</translation>
                <original>はい</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="372" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:18:37,068</start-time>
                <end-time>00:18:40,115</end-time>
                <translation>也就是说 对于命运 总该有什么对策吧</translation>
                <original>つまり運命に対して何か策があるだろうと</original>
                <spell/>
