                <start-time>00:21:35,775</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:39,281</end-time>
                <translation>拼命地展示自己在政治世界里是多么有用的人</translation>
                <original>自分がいかに政治の世界で役に立つ人間であるか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="438" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:39,281</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:42,035</end-time>
                <translation>也就是在拼命地推销自己</translation>
                <original>ということを一生懸命アピールしているわけなんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="439" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:42,035</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:44,814</end-time>
                <translation>就是“请一定要任用我”的意思呢</translation>
                <original>自分をぜひ使ってくださいということですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="440" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:44,814</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:46,288</end-time>
                <translation>那么 我们可以说</translation>
                <original>じゃあこれはいわば</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="441" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:46,288</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:49,224</end-time>
                <translation>《君主论》是一篇为了求职的论文</translation>
                <original>君主論というのは就職のための論文</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="442" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:49,224</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:50,680</end-time>
                <translation>这么也可以么？</translation>
                <original>とも言えるんですかね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="443" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:50,680</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:51,960</end-time>
                <translation>没错</translation>
                <original>そうなんですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="444" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:51,960</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:53,562</end-time>
                <translation>他是想通过这部《君主论》</translation>
                <original>彼はこの君主論によって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="445" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:53,562</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:56,800</end-time>
                <translation>来开拓自己的命运</translation>
                <original>自分の運命を切り開いていこうとしていたんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="446" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:56,800</start-time>
                <end-time>00:21:59,835</end-time>
                <translation>所以 他在失势后仅仅几个月</translation>
                <original>だから失脚して本当に数ヶ月</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="447" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:21:59,835</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:02,758</end-time>
                <translation>很短的时间内就写完了</translation>
                <original>という短い期間の間に書き上げてしまったんですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="448" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:02,758</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:04,482</end-time>
                <translation>是在那么短的时间内写成的吗？</translation>
                <original>そんな短い間に書いたんですか</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="449" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:04,482</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:06,675</end-time>
                <translation>他给朋友</translation>
                <original>彼はその友人に対して</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="450" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:06,675</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:09,236</end-time>
                <translation>留下了这样一句话</translation>
                <original>実はこんな言葉を残しているんです</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="451" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:09,236</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:09,974</end-time>
                <translation>好</translation>
                <original>はい</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="452" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:13,203</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:16,360</end-time>
                <translation>我爱我的祖国 胜过爱我的灵魂</translation>
                <original>我が魂よりも我が祖国を愛します</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="453" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:21,364</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:24,860</end-time>
                <translation>也就是说 为祖国的和平而工作</translation>
                <original>つまりこれは祖国の平和のために働くことが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="454" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:24,860</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:27,315</end-time>
                <translation>对他来说是最大的喜悦</translation>
                <original>彼にとって一番の喜びだった</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="455" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:27,315</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:29,464</end-time>
                <translation>所以想尽快回到现场</translation>
                <original>だから現場に早く戻りたい</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="456" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:29,464</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:30,947</end-time>
                <translation>这个意思吧</translation>
                <original>ということなんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="457" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:30,947</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:35,952</end-time>
                <translation>总而言之 即便牺牲自己 也要切实守护自己的国家</translation>
                <original>とにかく自分を犠牲にしてまでも自分の国をちゃんと守り</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="458" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:35,952</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:38,840</end-time>
                <translation>并且思考其发展 像这样的</translation>
                <original>そしてその育成を考えていきますというような</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="459" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:38,840</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:40,572</end-time>
                <translation>一种表态吧 这是</translation>
                <original>表明ですよね、これね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="460" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:40,572</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:44,389</end-time>
                <translation>能看出他非常拼命和专一的一面呢</translation>
                <original>非常に一生懸命で一途さが出ているというのが出ていますよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="461" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:44,389</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:45,008</end-time>
                <translation>是的</translation>
                <original>はい</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="462" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:45,008</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:46,060</end-time>
                <translation>他真是个热血的人啊</translation>
                <original>熱い人だったんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="463" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:46,060</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:47,586</end-time>
                <translation>确实是个热血的人</translation>
                <original>熱い人ですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="464" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:47,586</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:49,217</end-time>
                <translation>对于自己认为是君主的人
自分の君主と思う人には</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="465" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:49,217</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:51,787</end-time>
                <translation>希望他能具备这些要素呢</translation>
                <original>こういう要素を持っていてほしいということですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="466" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:51,787</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:54,767</end-time>
                <translation>从某种意义上说 能如此直率地说出这些</translation>
                <original>ある意味こういうことをストレートに言えるというのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="467" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:54,767</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:57,125</end-time>
                <translation>这种简单和直率</translation>
                <original>シンプルさストレートさというのが</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="468" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:57,125</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:58,627</end-time>
                <translation>为了让国家变好</translation>
                <original>国を良くするためには</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="469" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:22:58,627</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:00,420</end-time>
                <translation>或许是非常必要的呢</translation>
                <original>とても必要なことなのかもしれませんね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="470" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:00,420</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:01,228</end-time>
                <translation>是的呢</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="471" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:01,228</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:02,718</end-time>
                <translation>好</translation>
                <original>はい</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="472" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:02,718</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:03,900</end-time>
                <translation>老师 今天非常感谢您</translation>
                <original>先生今日ははありがとうございました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="473" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:03,900</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:05,597</end-time>
                <translation>- 非常感谢
- 非常感谢</translation>
                <original>-ありがとうございました　-ありがとうございました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="474" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:09,078</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:12,020</end-time>
                <translation>马基雅维利是个实干家呢</translation>
                <original>本当にマキャベリーって実行の人だというのはよくわかりましたよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="475" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:12,020</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:12,500</end-time>
                <translation>是的呢</translation>
                <original>そうですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="476" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:12,500</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:15,155</end-time>
                <translation>放在今天 就是为了日本</translation>
                <original>今でいうと日本のために</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="477" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:15,155</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:17,179</end-time>
                <translation>去会见美国、英国、中国、</translation>
                <original>例えばアメリカ、イギリス、中国、</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="478" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:17,179</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:20,344</end-time>
                <translation>印度、俄罗斯等各国的领导人</translation>
                <original>インド、ロシアといろんなリーダーにあって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="479" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:20,344</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:23,659</end-time>
                <translation>把那些经验全部总结起来 提交给日本的领导人</translation>
                <original>それを全部経験まとめて日本のリーダーに提出すると</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="480" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:23,659</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:24,579</end-time>
                <translation>告诉他们这样做国家就会变好</translation>
                <original>こうやれば国が良くなるんですよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="481" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:24,579</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:26,588</end-time>
                <translation>就是那么回事吧 在现代的话</translation>
                <original>そういうことですよね現代でいうと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="482" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:26,588</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:28,714</end-time>
                <translation>如果日本也有那样的人就好了呢</translation>
                <original>そういう人がいればね日本にもね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="483" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:28,714</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:31,392</end-time>
                <translation>是的呢 那样就让人安心多了</translation>
                <original>そうですね心強いですよね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="484" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:31,392</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:32,798</end-time>
                <translation>真不愧是马基雅维利的《君主论》</translation>
                <original>本当にマキャベリーの君主論</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="485" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:32,798</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:35,940</end-time>
                <translation>那么 下一回的主题是“领导者的条件”</translation>
                <original>さあ次回はですねリーダーの条件とは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="486" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:35,940</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:39,460</end-time>
                <translation>我们将以此为题 解读《君主论》中所描绘的领导者形象</translation>
                <original>と題しまして君主論に描かれたリーダー像</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="487" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:39,460</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:41,335</end-time>
                <translation>及其心得</translation>
                <original>この心得を解いてまいります</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="488" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:41,335</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:44,080</end-time>
                <translation>我相信其中一定有对大家都有益的教诲</translation>
                <original>必ず皆さんの役に立つ教えがあると思いますよ</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="489" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:44,080</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:45,560</end-time>
                <translation>敬请期待下一回</translation>
                <original>次回もどうぞお楽しみに</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t index="490" hasRuby="0" id="" time="" vertical="0" torder="1">
                <start-time>00:23:57,780</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:58,000</end-time>
                <translation>感谢您的收看</translation>
                <original>ご視聴ありがとうございました</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
